 /></blockquote><br />\n唉 好似美國咁 就算個政府唔肯加多啲配套 哈佛都肯去整個新系統比人借單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實英國嗰啲周街都有得租單車，冇記錯係兩鎊24個鐘，見到好多人都有踩，踩埋上行人路都得。<br />\n你試吓可唔可以響彌敦道踩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以話唔係香港人唔想 只不過太多阻礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真如果成功整到我會好樂易踩單車"},{"pid":"9605ddb245ac21751be3c22e843805d6c4cd64c4","tid":367141,"uid":34473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再講起幾多條單車徑都冇用啦，響市區啲大陸人隨時當埋行人路咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n強烈要求單車徑踩車撞到行人，踩車者免責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b130c9fcd9d2e65daac9e3ec2c5c50360a2a09a","tid":367141,"uid":124941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"根本唔應該有私家車"},{"pid":"18346de540f1d4d05cc9501ed39f15056b7f3dc2","tid":367141,"uid":59006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔應該有私家車</blockquote><br />\n波大冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfd502f06a160ee8dbc4fb9624df317bb5e209a","tid":367141,"uid":13586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"絕對係，非常agree<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但無論設施，配套，宣傳，公民意識<br />\n全部都唔掂嘅時候，踩條毛？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRK8EdpL26vZMmpJR2M9uZmFza0NxalbEuv133SBO5lmGyKCJVKYA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcRK8EdpL26vZMmpJR2M9uZmFza0NxalbEuv133SBO5lmGyKCJVKYA&h=8ae3bc59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好講到新界單車徑未駁通由屯門踩到沙田，定港島九龍開路俾單車，淨係上面幅圖咁撚樣，踩撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"